text: As announced by FM Retno Marsudi @Menlu_RI, a total of 1.8 mln doses of #COVID19 #vaccine made by #China's #Sinovac Biotech arrived ystd (31/12), which is the 2nd batch of the Sinovac vaccine delivery for #Indonesia. The 1st batch of 1.2 mln doses arrived on December 6, 2020. https://t.co/2wrcZUO4uB
